pd_0_com_0text: More customers comes and goes. They buy various drinks, letting you get plenty of practice.
pd_0_com_1text: As the day goes on, there were some more customers who seemed to be rather engrossed in their mobile devices.
pd_0_com_2text: A lot of them had a frown on their expression. From the soft chatter you pick up here and there, it sounds like something unpleasant is happening in the news.
pd_0_com_3text: However, that is no concern for you. Your job is to make people happy with your drinks. If there is something that troublesome ...
pd_0_com_4text: Well, that's for future you to deal with.
pd_1_com_0text: You notice a familiar figure enter the cafe. She is also captivated by her phone with a worried expression on her face.
pd_1_com_1text: However, she let out a soft sigh before putting away the phone as she approaches the counter and fgives you a small smile.
pd_2_com_0text: Good evening. Nice to see you again.
pd_3_com_0text: It's my pleasure. How can I help you today?
pd_3_com_2text: Hello! Everyone and their phones today ...
pd_4_com_0text: She hesitates a moment, as if expecting something else. However, she quickly recovers as she places a finger on her lips.
pd_5_com_0text: I liked my drink from yesterday. Can I get it again? The boba Matcha Milk Tea with 100% milk?
pd_6_com_0text: Hmm ... It's not that big of a deal. Just worrying news I guess.
pd_6_com_1text: Things will probably be fine ... The media is known for overinflating stuff after all ...
pd_7_com_0text: Ah ... Yeah there has been some alarming news lately. Not that you need to worry I think. No one would harm a cute girl like you.
pd_7_com_1text: Haha well, you probably already know about it from reading on your own.
pd_8_com_0text: Oh ... I see. I'm sure everything will be ok.
pd_8_com_1text: You seem more worried than some of the other customers. [-2]
pd_8_com_2text: Even so ... take care of yourself ok? [+3]
pd_9_com_0text: Yeah, it'll be fine. In any case ... What should I order today ...
pd_10_com_0text: She nods and musters up a smile, though she didn't seem very confident about it.
pd_11_com_0text: She blinks and seems to stiffen up a bit, before looking away, rubbing her forearm awkwardly.
pd_12_com_1text: Mmm ... Well ... Perhaps I'm a bit more worried than others I suppose. But it's not really that big of a deal ... Don't worry yourself about it.
pd_12_com_2text: In any case ... I suppose I shouldn't keep you too long. Let's see ...
pd_13_com_0text: She looks rather surprised for a moment before giving you a genuinely sweet smile.
pd_14_com_0text: You're ... a kind person aren't you?
pd_15_com_0text: She seems to think for a moment before looking back at you, her eyes seeming a bit brighter than before.
pd_16_com_0text: Thank you for your concern. I think ... things will be fine.
pd_16_com_1text: Yeah ... I'll be sure to take care of myself. I'd hate to not be able to come back here and taste more of your delicious milk teas after all.
pd_18_com_0text: She still seems distracted when you go to give her the drink, though she gives you a smile and nod of thank before taking the drink.
pd_18_com_1text: She takes a long sip before giving the drink a soft smile, proceeding to direct that smile towards you.
pd_19_com_2text: I asked for a boba Matcha Milk Tea with 100% milk.
pd_21_com_0text: There is a visible red hue on her cheeks.
pd_22_com_1text: You shouldn't just tell that to any girl you meet ... You know ...
pd_23_com_0text: After a moment, she eases up and let out a soft giggle.
pd_24_com_0text: You're quite bold ... but thank you, I appreciate it.
pd_24_com_1text: Sorry about the awkwardness today, I'll try to have something better to talk about next time.
pd_26_com_0text: You stand there quietly for a moment before your eyes brighten, as if remembering something. She seems to notice it as well.
pd_28_com_0text: She seems a bit startled before touching her cheek embarassedly.
pd_29_com_0text: Oh! How rude of me ... I forgot to introduce myself properly all this time.
pd_30_com_0text: I'm Elya! Some of my friends just call me Ely, which is fine too.
pd_30_com_1text: Well, I'll be heading out nice. It's been nice talking with you again. See you later!
pd_31_com_0text: With a wave, she left with another sip of her drink. With you greeting the next customer, you wouldn't notice the brief glance that Elya gave toward the cafe before disappearing into the city.
pd_31_com_1text: As the day goes on, less people seem to be whispering about their phones and walking around with concerned expressions.
pd_31_com_2text: The day soon comes to close. While the amount of customers that came wasn't more than the previous, it definitely felt more eventful.
pd_31_com_3text: While some of the events weren't exactly the best perhaps, you did get to learn more about some of your customers. When they come back, hopefully you'll get even more interesting conversations.
pd_31_com_4text: For now, you simply clean up and get the store ready for the next day.
